The base strategy is to get all 5 pieces of Exodia into your hand on your first turn (does not haver to be on the first turn to win). This is the base strategy.

&nbsp;

Play Numeron Network and either use its effect to activate or activate Numeron Calling from your hand. Summon all 4 Numeron XYZ monsters for the extra deck. Then you can activate Memories of Hope to draw 4 cards for free. Then you use the 4 Numeron XYZ monsters to summon Saryuja Skull Dread. Then activate its effect to draw 4 cards and the shuffle 3 back into the deck. Then you can activate Link Bound and draw 4 cards to shuffle 4 back into the deck. Don't worry if you don't have Exodia. There are many more ways than this to draw from your deck.

